	<h1>Nihilism</h1>
	
	<blockquote cite="https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Friedrich_Nietzsche#Quotes">
		<p>There are no facts, only interpretations - <i>Friedrich Nietzsche</i></p>
	</blockquote>
	
		<p>Nihilism requires the rejection of all religious and moral principles.
		   This ideology believes that life is meaningless.</p>
		   
		   
